{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"85de394b69","title":"中南军政委员会关于干部在土地改革工作时期的八项纪律","origin":"根据文件的原件打印","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"df0094143b","index":0,"year":1950,"month":12,"day":2,"articleId":"85de394b69"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-shzygz","name":"中国五十年代初中期的政治运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-shzygz":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"d68601acf0","type":"title","text":"中南军政委员会关于干部在土地改革工作时期的八项纪律","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"85de394b69"},{"id":"cc20e4d0a9","type":"paragraph","text":"一、严格执行政府法令，认真掌握土地改革路线，依靠雇贫团结中农，不得违犯。","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"85de394b69"},{"id":"94f3f4fa0a","type":"paragraph","text":"二、坚决保护农民利益，不得包庇地主，不得附和地主叫嚣。","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"85de394b69"},{"id":"4a944a9724","type":"paragraph","text":"三、依法严惩不法地主，坚决领导群众开展合法斗争，打击地主抵抗与破坏行为，防止乱打、乱杀。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"85de394b69"},{"id":"46c7803e47","type":"paragraph","text":"四、明确划清敌我界线，不得丧失立场，制造与参加乡村宗派纠纷。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"85de394b69"},{"id":"4505d2d595","type":"paragraph","text":"五、绝对禁止贪污受贿，廉洁奉公，艰苦朴素，不得侵占斗争果实，不得假公济私。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"85de394b69"},{"id":"1c795dac04","type":"paragraph","text":"六、切实服从农协决议，尊重农民意见，凡事要和群众商量，不要个人决定，强迫推行。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"85de394b69"},{"id":"95845f7901","type":"paragraph","text":"七、坚决服从上级指示，不得阳奉阴违，不得各自为政。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"85de394b69"},{"id":"4941f7d5f9","type":"paragraph","text":"八、严格请示报告制度，不得虚报情况，不得报喜不报忧。","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"85de394b69"}],"page":{"id":"e32a3ec645","publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"85de394b69","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}